{"tid":933910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綠色和平走塑專員半年前分別去咗8大連鎖快餐店發現大部分都「假走塑，真浪費」！！！","createTime":"2018-12-08T21:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T16:04:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"63bf9d373b82a4dcb93e73c8fc345c3369a23f1f","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T21:23:57.000Z","msg":"【 #本周焦點- 走塑實測2】<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平走塑專員半年前分別去咗8大連鎖快餐店進行走塑實測，發現大部分都「假走塑，真浪費」👀 半年後，我哋再去到大家樂、大快活實測，想知佢哋有冇真正走塑？去片啦👇！睇完之後大家一齊全民監察，留言分享或者影低你嗰區大家樂、大快活嘅走塑實況，舉報全派膠嘅分店！<br />\n<br />\n回顧半年前嘅走塑實測👉 <a href=\"https://act.gp/2vYKJ9n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact.gp%2F2vYKJ9n&d=PezPnMxezpw6vaA5v8md6xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a7fb2b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act.gp/2vYKJ9n</a><br />\n<br />\n#夠鐘走塑 #PlasticFreeNow<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/videos/1876408135997824/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenpeacehk%2Fvideos%2F1876408135997824%2F&d=PezPnMxezpw6vaA5v8md6xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=daa16f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/videos/1876408135997824/</a>"},{"pid":"8eca859a2468d8f949de5e6c67dc420c1671b3b4","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T21:25:07.000Z","msg":"即係咁,我唔介意你叫人環保<br />\n但係d野發明出嚟,係因為果樣野有需要先會有人發明<br />\n你就淨係一味叫人唔好用,但係又無替代方案<br />\n好似飲筒咁,牙齒敏感嘅人點樣就咁倒凍飲落口吖？<br />\n而且飲筒個問題係胡亂棄置,解決方法係唔用？<br />\n呢d只係斬腳趾避沙蟲囉。"},{"pid":"0a40dbf018d9787ba858e1b79b266c662e71422e","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T21:25:27.000Z","msg":"紅豆冰都走筒?環保狗真係呢..."},{"pid":"d899b7263503573826373f9c98659b288883a95c","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T21:31:01.000Z","msg":"認同 宜家為響應假環保 令市民帶來極多不便 真係環保 我不便一下又有咩所為 但好多時 都係表面好環保 實情係浪費既 比宜家支持緊環保成成果 還要多 咁 做咩仲要假環保大不便呢 <br />\n好似節約用水 要慳環保 愛惜地球 <br />\n一邊就慳住慳住用 另一邊就數以唔知幾多加輪咁倒入海 咁環咩保? 荷包環保?<br />\n環保唔代表係平或慳錢 想環保就要附出 搵唔到解決既辦法就 要落多啲成本去解決 唔係唔用 就了左件事 教壞細路吖"},{"pid":"7b92a5df6ce8c2a5ac02b63ba2227bd5c82158e2","tid":933910,"uid":97398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"假環保撚從來都唔會實際上解決問題，最好就大家過返原始人嘅生活"},{"pid":"cbabe6f5d02598a6e2c49079fa1c675ed360991c","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb5ba956ffd74cda4348e09bf78fd05c973f0fd","tid":933910,"uid":103325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"你地搞咁多嘢，無非都係想要一句「多謝支持環保」同攞少少認同感啫"},{"pid":"c7fac0f411db47e0b0aa8be24acb817401d4c272","tid":933910,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:08:53.000Z","msg":"綠膠真係煩<br />\n做又唔得唔做又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad340cb92bd6680bb80cbd86eba7a6c4df476df9","tid":933910,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"5df57e1dad4ce1faae2d391c31cca013cc50a5ea","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b9d6ff40189a64cc6661c891d2e915a97b925d","tid":933910,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T21:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f10579aa236f15c2bf91395747c1ecb3604f2b","tid":933910,"uid":34205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T23:11:17.000Z","msg":"本身班撚樣未搞咁多on9 嘢出嚟之前我都會唔攞飲筒同杯蓋，但係自從見到啲廣告之後就無再做呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdb21edb8af4adc7d1d416b850d04425ac445e4","tid":933910,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score